{
  "stem": "24651.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think that, I think that actually might have happened, because I, I have this-- I, I sort of remember seeing her one time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because then I went to live with this woman Maria.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she-- we went by train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I, I don't remember how this whole thing was explained to me, except I know that it was-- I knew that it was very, very serious, and I knew that I had to do what I was told and that-- and I went by train with her.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And during the train ride I had to be quiet and not really say much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, and then I went to her apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember the apartment because it was-- she left me there at night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was very frightened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She'd, you know, she'd go out in the evening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was no electricity, so it was pitch black.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it was in a very main, main thoroughfare.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I saw the lights, and I remember the streetcars going by.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, and I remember being kind of panicky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was, you know, crying and trying all the doors, and everything was locked up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was the only person there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- well, one other thing I recalled at that-- during my stay there, at one time the Gestapo came.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a, a, a man, very blond, very good-looking with black leather boots.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came running upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was looking for Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he asked who I was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The woman said I was her niece, that I, I, you know, my, my mother, her sister was ill and she was taking care of me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he ransacked the whole apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He pulled out all the drawers from the furniture.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
